{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "第四回\"赤手歼魔\"讲述了燕南天寻找二弟江枫途中，先救下被苍鹰追击的弱燕，随后听到婴儿啼哭赶到江枫遇害现场。沈轻虹与镖师钱二、雷啸虎等待十二星相的到来，钱二临阵脱逃，雷啸虎义无反顾追随沈轻虹。金猿星率黑狗星等人现身，以灵猴献果、神犬迎客之名威吓，沈轻虹以\"飞花满天\"暗器击退灵猴。危急时刻燕南天从天而降，赤手撕碎黑犬星等六人，威震全场。金猿星以言语激将，透露江琴出卖江枫、三千两银子卖主求荣的真相，并指出江琴投奔之地——昆仑山恶人谷。燕南天怒挖金猿星双眼，携江枫遗孤前往太白居，买棺收殓江枫与月奴尸身，灌注香料防腐。末段燕南天抱着婴儿路遇哺乳期农妇，求其为婴儿哺乳，得知婴儿母亲已死，农妇慨然相助，婴儿在温暖中露出幸福微笑。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奇怪，二弟已在道上，我怎地听不见……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兀那恶鹰，你难道也像人间恶徒一般，欺凌弱小……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好恶鹰，你逃得过燕某之手，算你有种！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "二弟呀二弟．你瞧瞧我赤手落鹰的威风！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好燕儿，乖燕儿，忍着些，你不会死的……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "燕儿呀燕儿，你已耽误我不少时候，你若能飞，就快快去吧。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "万两黄金，不能令我耽误片刻，不想这小燕子却拖住我了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非二弟已有了娃儿？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_er",
      "speaker_name": "钱二",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "不知总镖头和那'十二星相'约在何时？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就是今日黄昏。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_er",
      "speaker_name": "钱二",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "今晚！……在哪里？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就在前面！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_er",
      "speaker_name": "钱二",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "他……他们有多少人？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "星辰帖上具名的，乃是黑面、司晨、献果、迎客、偷泉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_er",
      "speaker_name": "钱二",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "难……难道，鸡、猪、猴、狗一齐出手？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_er",
      "speaker_name": "钱二",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "总镖头，咱们还是走吧，凭咱们，只……只怕……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们走吧。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_er",
      "speaker_name": "钱二",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "总镖头你……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "镖主以义待我，沈轻虹岂能无义报之，你们……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_er",
      "speaker_name": "钱二",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "总镖头……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_xiao_hu",
      "speaker_name": "雷啸虎",
      "listener": "char_qian_er",
      "text": "怎么？你不去么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_er",
      "speaker_name": "钱二",
      "listener": "char_lei_xiao_hu",
      "text": "让他从容就义去吧，咱们可犯不着去送死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_xiao_hu",
      "speaker_name": "雷啸虎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "畜生……你们作畜生，我雷啸虎可不能陪你们作畜生。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_er",
      "speaker_name": "钱二",
      "listener": "char_lei_xiao_hu",
      "text": "好，好，我是畜生，你是义士。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_xiao_hu",
      "speaker_name": "雷啸虎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "畜生，畜生，我今日才算认得你们……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是雷啸虎么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_xiao_hu",
      "speaker_name": "雷啸虎",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "总镖头，是我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我早已知道只有你一人会来的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_xiao_hu",
      "speaker_name": "雷啸虎",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "听总镖头这句话，雷啸虎死也甘心，我雷啸虎虽然是呆子，却非无耻的畜生，但……但总镖头，你……你这次……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": "char_lei_xiao_hu",
      "text": "你是奇怪我为何不多约人来么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_xiao_hu",
      "speaker_name": "雷啸虎",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "正是有些奇怪。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": "char_lei_xiao_hu",
      "text": "十二星相，各有奇功，江湖友辈中能胜过他们的人并不多，我若约了朋友，别人为了义气，虽想不来，也不能不来，但我又怎忍心令朋友们为难、送死？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_xiao_hu",
      "speaker_name": "雷啸虎",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "总镖头毕竟是总镖头，我雷啸虎纵然有总镖头这样的武功，也休想能做得上三大镖局的总镖头，我……",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_xiao_hu",
      "speaker_name": "雷啸虎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非来……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_xiao_hu",
      "speaker_name": "雷啸虎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这'十二星相'，果然邪门……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "十二星相专喜作诡异，为的就是先声夺人，先寒敌胆，咱们莫被他骗住，折了锐气！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_xiao_hu",
      "speaker_name": "雷啸虎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不怕，谁怕谁就是孙子！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "十二星相在哪里？洛阳沈轻虹前来拜见！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好一个'神犬迎客，灵猴献果'，但是沈轻虹会的是'十二星相'中的人，却不是这些畜生！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "'十二星相'若是鸩人的鼠辈，沈轻虹今日也不会来了……沈轻虹信得过你们，纵是毒药，也要吃下！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lei_xiao_hu",
      "speaker_name": "雷啸虎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要钱的桃子，不吃岂非冤枉！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，无怪'三远镖旗'能畅行大河两岸，镖局中果然还有两个有胆子的好汉……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来的想必是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "咱们的模样，你自然一瞧就知道，还用得着说么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "text": "在下只是奇怪，怎地少了黑面君与司晨客？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "他两人去做另一票买卖去了，有我们这几人，你还嫌不够么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈轻虹今日反正是一个人来的，反正已没打算活着回去，能多瞧见几位'十二星相'的真面目，固然不错，少瞧见几个，也不觉遗憾。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "我知道你胆子不小，却不知道你口才竟也不错，但你辛辛苦苦爬上总镖头的宝座并不容易．死了岂非冤枉。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "text": "沈轻虹此来并非与你逞口舌之强。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "你想打？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "text": "正是！沈某若胜，只望各位休想再打镖货的主意……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "败了又如何？将镖货双手送上么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那批红货早已由我家副总镖头'双鞭'宋德扬加急送上去了，沈某此来，不过是声东击西，调虎离山而已。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "你瞧瞧这是什么！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你竟……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "'十二星相'若是常常被骗的人，江湖中人也不会瞧见咱们那么头疼了……老实告诉你，那批红货，早已落入咱们手中，咱们此来，不过只是要你的命罢了！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不想三远镖局的大镖头们，竟连两只畜生也打不过！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪里走！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好个'飞花满天'，果然有两下子！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "燕大侠来了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非是燕南天？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "十二星相，你们的死期到了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "十二星相与你无冤无仇，你为何……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "站住！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还要某家动手不成？！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "你……你为什么……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "text": "为什么？你可知道江枫是某家的什么人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "莫非那……那只猪已……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "text": "别人都已死了，你活着又有何趣味，纳命来吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "text": "不想你个子虽小，倒还是条汉子，若是换了平日，某家也能饶你一命，但今日……哼，你还有何话说？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "你个子虽大，却也算不得是大丈夫。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "text": "某家这一生行事，虽得天下之名，却也有不少人骂我，善恶本不两立，那也算不得什么，但你这句话，某家倒要听听你是凭什么说出来的。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "是非不明，恩仇不辨，算得了大丈夫么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "text": "某家……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "你若是明辨是非之辈，便不该杀我。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "text": "为何不该杀你？我二弟江枫……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "这就对了，你若为别的事杀我，那我无话可说，但你若为江枫杀我，你便是不明是非，不辨恩仇。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "'十二星相'难道未曾对我二弟江枫出手？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "不错，'十二星相'确曾向江枫出手，但'十二星相'本是强盗，这一点你早已知道，强盗要劫人钱财，本是分内之事，既是分内之事便算不得什么深仇大恨，那前来通风报讯，要'十二星相'向江枫出手的，才是你真正要复仇的对象，你可知道他是谁么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "前来通风报汛的，莫非是江琴那小畜生？我二弟之行程，只有那小畜生一个人知道。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "不错，原来你非但四肢发达，头脑也不简单，江枫的确是被他视为心腹的人卖了，三千两银子就卖了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "畜生……畜生……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "那畜生此刻在哪里，你可知道？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "text": "你知道他在哪里，是么？",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "我若不知道，这些话就不说了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "text": "他在哪里？说！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "text": "你若不说，我佩服你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "我……我说了又如何？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "text": "你说了，我便挖出你一双眼睛！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "虽然没有眼睛，但只要能活着，也就罢了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "text": "说吧！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "只是我说出了，你也未必敢去。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "普天之下，还没有燕某不敢去的地方！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "那江琴不是呆子，明知我'十二星相'杀人不过如同踩死只蚂蚁，他拿了'十二星相'的银子，难道不怕脑袋搬家？他如此大胆，只因他早已有投奔之地，拿这银子，正是要用作路费，而他那投奔之地，'十二星相'加在一起，也不敢走近那地方半步。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "移花宫？……某家正要去的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "当今天下，也未必只有'移花宫'是武林禁地。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "text": "除了'移花宫'还有哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "昆仑山，'恶人谷'……",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "燕大侠，你……你去不得！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "text": "你说的可是真话？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "我话已说出，信不信都由得你了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "那'恶人谷'乃是天下恶人聚集之地，那些人没有一个不是十恶不赦，满手血腥；没有一个不是被江湖中人恨之入骨。但那许多恶人聚在一起，别人纵然恨不得吃他们的肉，也没有人敢走近'恶人谷'一步，就连'昆仑七剑'、'少林四神僧'、'江南剑客'风啸雨，都也……也不敢……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "燕南天既非少林神僧，也非江南剑客！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "我知道燕大侠你剑术当代无双，但那'恶人谷'……那谷中成千成百，也不知究竟有多少的恶人……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "义之所在，燕某何惧赴汤蹈火！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "但说不定这根本是金猿星故意骗你的，他已对你恨之入骨，所以要你到那恶人谷去送……送……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "恶人谷纵是刀山火海，也未必能要了燕南天的命！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！燕南天果然是英雄！竟连'恶人谷'也敢闯上一闯，你此去纵然有去无还，也必将博得天下武林佩服！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "text": "你还有何话呢？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "没有了，拿我的眼珠去吧！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "text": "你金猿星纵然一世聪明，今日却做了件笨事。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "我笨？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "text": "燕南天虽未取你性命，但将你送到我手中，我还会饶你？……你片刻纵有灵药治伤，又有何用！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "自然有用，我死不了的！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "text": "还有谁能救你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "我自己。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "text": "沈某倒要瞧瞧你如何能救你自己……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "那镖银你不想要了么？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "我早就算准你不敢动手杀我的，你若想要镖银，只有我能给你，除非你有这胆子不要镖银。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "算你赢了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yuan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "金猿星",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "沈轻虹，如今你可知道了吧！无论谁想杀我，都没有那么容易！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁说我要酒？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "酒保",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "大爷不……不要酒，要什么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "米汤！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "酒保",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "小店不……不卖……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "先去煮几碗浓浓的米汤，再拿酒来。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "去替我买些东西来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "酒保",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "大……大爷要买什么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "棺材！两口上好的棺材！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "棺材，两口上好的棺材，听到了么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiu_bao",
      "speaker_name": "酒保",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "听……听……听……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 518,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "听到了还不快去！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "半个时辰后你等便可无碍，香料银价，来日加倍奉还！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 548,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nong_jia_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "农家少妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这孩子的娘不在么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不在。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nong_jia_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "农家少妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来他是饿了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是饿了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nong_jia_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "农家少妇",
      "listener": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "text": "把你的孩子抱过来吧，我来喂他，反正这几天我吃了两只鸡，奶水正足，咱们小妞儿也吃不了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": "char_nong_jia_shao_fu",
      "text": "多谢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nong_jia_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "农家少妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们带孩子真该小心些，这孩子的娘也真是，竟放心把这么小的孩子交给你一个大男人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 582,
      "line_end": 582
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_nan_tian",
      "speaker_name": "燕南天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这孩子的娘已死了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_nong_jia_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "农家少妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "从小就没有娘的孩子，真是可怜。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 588
    }
